---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Donate | Christen Thompson for Heber City Council</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen font-sans">
    <header class="bg-green-900 text-white py-6 shadow">
      <div
        class="container mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between px-4"
      >
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">
          <a href="/" class="hover:underline"
            >Christen Thompson for Heber City Council</a
          >
        </h1>
        <nav class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
          <a href="/" class="mr-6 hover:underline">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="mr-6 hover:underline">About</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="mr-6 hover:underline">Blog</a>
          <a href="/donate" class="hover:underline">Donate</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Support Our Community</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
            Instead of donating to my campaign, please consider donating to
            these organizations that are working to protect our open spaces,
            trails, and natural resources in Utah:
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-green-800">
                Wasatch Trail Foundation
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Dedicated to building and maintaining trails in the Wasatch
                Mountains, connecting communities through outdoor recreation.
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://wasatchtrails.org"
                class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors"
                target="_blank"
              >
                Donate to Wasatch Trails
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-green-800">
                Utah Open Lands
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Protecting Utah's open spaces through conservation easements and
                land preservation for future generations.
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://utahopenlands.org/"
                class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors"
                target="_blank"
              >
                Donate to Utah Open Lands
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-green-800">
                Summit Land Conservancy
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Preserving open space and natural lands in Summit County through
                conservation easements and community partnerships.
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://summitlandconservancy.org/"
                class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors"
                target="_blank"
              >
                Donate to Summit Land Conservancy
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-green-800">
                Southern Utah Wilderness Alliance
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Protecting Utah's wild places and advocating for wilderness
                preservation across the state.
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://suwa.org/"
                class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors"
                target="_blank"
              >
                Donate to SUWA
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-800">
              Why These Organizations?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              These organizations align with my campaign platform of protecting
              open space, clean air, clean water, and creating better trails and
              paths. By supporting them, you're helping to preserve the natural
              beauty of Utah and Heber Valley for future generations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="bg-green-900 text-white py-4 mt-10 text-center">
      &copy; 2025 Christen Thompson for Heber City Council
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
